---
import type { MajorRelease, MinorRelease } from "../data/release-types";

type Props = {
  majorRelease: MajorRelease;
  latestRelease: MinorRelease;
  totalReleaseCount: number;
  majorLineCount: number;
};

const { majorRelease, latestRelease, totalReleaseCount, majorLineCount } = Astro.props;
---

<header class="archive-intro" aria-labelledby="archive-title">
  <p class="archive-intro__eyebrow">
    <span class="brand-mark" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    Java Edition · Official releases
  </p>
  <h1 id="archive-title">Minecraft Version Archive</h1>
  <p class="archive-intro__lead">
    Minecraft Java Edition 정식 릴리즈의 전체 기록입니다. {majorLineCount}개의 메이저 버전 라인에
    걸친 {totalReleaseCount}개의 정식 릴리즈를 최신순으로 정리했습니다.
  </p>

  <section class="latest-callout" aria-label="Most recent release">
    <div class="latest-callout__head">
      <span class="latest-callout__tag">Latest</span>
      <span class="latest-callout__version">{latestRelease.version}</span>
      <span class={`release-label release-label--${latestRelease.label}`}>
        {latestRelease.label}
      </span>
      <time class="latest-callout__date" datetime={latestRelease.releasedAt}>
        {latestRelease.releasedAt}
      </time>
    </div>
    <p class="latest-callout__summary">{latestRelease.summary}</p>
    <p class="latest-callout__line">{majorRelease.version} · {majorRelease.name}</p>
  </section>
</header>
